title: Nidhogg [Wineskin]
description:
Name: Nidhogg
Year: 2014
Genre: Action, Indie
Kind: Wineskin
Rating: 9/10 on IGN

Description:
Nidhogg is the epic award-winning fencing tug-of-war, full of graceful acrobatics and clumsy stabs. IRL yelling and excitement may occur, in this ultimate two-player showdown of fast-paced fencing and melee attacks. Beware, advantages in Nidhogg are often fleeting, as new opponents continually spawn in your way.

Instructions: Unzip and Play

Notes: The game is not online enabled.  Although single player and offline multiplayer work fine.

OS: Tested and working on Mavericks and Yosemite.

If you like a game, please consider supporting the devs by purchasing the game.
